generic:link.msg:message: Identity "Share Capital = (Ordinary Shares + Compulsory Convertible Preference Shares + Preference shares other than Compulsory Convertible)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Total Reserves and Surplus = (Capital Reserve + Capital Redemption Reserve + Debenture Redemption Reserve + Share Premium + General Reserves + Statutory/Special Reserve (Section 45-IC reserve to be shown separately below item no. + Reserves under Sec 45-IC of RBI Act 1934 + Revaluation Reserves + Investment Fluctuation Reserve + Balance of profit and loss account + Share Application Money Pending Allotment + Other Reserves (Please provide the details, if any))" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Secured Debentures = (Subscribed by Retail Investors + Subscribed by Mutual Funds + Subscribed by Banks + Subscribed by NBFCs + Subscribed by Insurance Companies + Subscribed by Pension Funds + Others)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Borrowings from Banks - Secured = Term Loans + Working Capital loans + Cash Credit + Overdraft)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Total Secured Borrowings = (Debentures + Deferred credits + Borrowings from Banks + Borrowings from FIs + Borrowings from Government (State and Central) + Govt. Guaranteed Borrowings + Borrowings from Public Sector Undertakings (PSUs) + Borrowings through CBLO/LAF + Borrowings from RBI + Other Borrowings + Interest accrued but not due on the above)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Unsecured Debentures = (Subscribed by Retail Investors + Subscribed by Mutual Funds + Subscribed by Banks + Subscribed by NBFCs + Subscribed by Insurance Companies + Subscribed by Pension Funds + Others)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Unsecured Borrowings = (Borrowings from relatives of promoters / directors + Inter-corporate borrowings + Borrowings from Banks + Borrowings from FIs + Borrowings from Public Sector Undertakings (PSUs) + Commercial paper + Debentures not in the nature of public deposit + Money received by way of caution money, margin money from the borrowers, lessee, hires or by way of security or advance from agents in the course of company's business or advance received against orders for supply of goods or properties or for redering services + Subordinated debts + Borrowings from Government + Govt. Guaranteed Borrowings + Call Money Borrowings + Borrowings from RBI + Borrowings from Holding Company + Other Borrowings + Interest accrued but not due on the above" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Total Borrowings = (Secured Borrowings + Un-Secured Borrowings)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Total Borrowings = (Borrowings payable more than 12 months + Borrowings payable more than 3 months but less than or equal to 12 months + Borrowings payable less than or equal to 3 months)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Total Current Liabilities = (Current Liabilities + Sundry Creditors + Liabilities to Subsidiaries & Holding Company + Deferred Tax Liabilities (Net) + Others)" do not tally.
